cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.GR 

This paper is about image deraining using deep learning networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper proposes a new network architecture and loss functions, which involves training the network using large datasets. This suggests that the paper may also belong to the categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper involves image processing, which may also suggest the category of cs.GR (Graphics).
